{"tid":1271452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"RTHK：警方建議遊行延期或改路線　籲大眾慎重考慮參與","createTime":"2019-07-01T06:24:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T06:25:49.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"be8925fece7b5c24730d5839efc9034a4e28e033","tid":1271452,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:24:55.000Z","msg":"金鐘有示威者衝擊立法會，警察公共關係科高級警司江永祥表示，強烈譴責有關示威者的暴力行為，對所有違法行為作出嚴肅追究。他說，基於安全理由，立法會不適宜作遊行終點。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，示威者以雜物霸佔、偷鐵支和磚塊等行為，並衝擊立法會，對警方構成危險，又對社會造成極壞影響，而今早有13名警員被不知名物體濺中亦受傷送院。<br />\n<br />\n被問及上午有警員撤退夏慤道一帶，江永祥說，警方現場作出的所有部署，都有考慮當時氣氛和風險評估，就立法會的暴力行為予以最嚴厲譴責，而調配警員因應示威者用的策略。<br />\n<br />\n中區警區總督察古兆輝說，現埸有暴力示威者，對於下午舉行的遊行活動會作出相關配合，警方向主辦單位作出建議，包括遊行延期舉行或更改遊行路線等，呼籲大眾要慎重考慮參與活動，安全最重要。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1465986-20190701.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1465986-20190701.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=IJ4Nzxd4hLWYFZk0XL5PgUcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=9d22cc22\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1465986-20190701.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=285f4f69\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1465986-20190701.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"baa15c9dc85952b84206e476323ac8144fe5cf16","tid":1271452,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:25:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">緊急！！！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請立即前往維園參與7.1大遊行！！！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UYwmWB6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUYwmWB6.jpg&h=5b9573bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qcfrog7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqcfrog7.jpg&h=67209b55&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}